name: Senior #20 - Dr. Colo
description:
Dr. Colo is a 72-year-old mad scientist with an avid fascination for chemistry, explosions, and soju bombs. Since he was young, he loved blowing shits up from small insects, his mom’s baked apple pies, to neighbour's chickens for casually cock-a-doodle-doing in the morning.

He is one of the Most Wanted bio-scientist criminals in the world. He has set his infamous prosthetic eye to create the ultimate weaponised bio-explosives dedicated to eradicate living things and ultimately, himself.

Lab location: Unknown
